summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Mary Avenue Northwest, from West Seventieth Street to West Seventy-fifth Street in the City of Seattle., by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 21195, creating Local Improvement District No. 2101 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
